==================================================================================

it's the simplest port scanner for a very specific scan of desired ports

[[FOR JAVA VERSION]]
$ cd src_java
$ javac PortChk.java
$ java PortChk
   ~ it should present you with a notification to provide CSV file
$ java PortChk sample_ports.csv


[[FOR RUBY VERSION]]
$ cd src_ruby
$ ruby slick_port_scanner.rb 
   ~ it should present you with a notification to provide CSV file
$ ruby slick_port_scanner.rb ../src_java/sample_ports.csv

==================================================================================
yet to be evolved a lot more, keeping the simple specific scan style intact
